# Title: Browser Execution In Headless Mode
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-09-12
# Level: low
# Description: Detects execution of Chromium based browser in headless mode
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.stealth, attack.t1105, attack.t1564.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_browsers_chromium_headless_exec.yml

CommandLine="*--headless*" Image IN ("*\\brave.exe", "*\\chrome.exe", "*\\msedge.exe", "*\\opera.exe", "*\\vivaldi.exe")